trans-unit.target: TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> Catty is looking over the food stores, her face a mask of concern.
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_TODO_00<tab>Slay two whiptails, then defeat the enraged Jaculus.
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_000<tab>This should be enough to last us. At least until those scaly buggers are taken care of...
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_001<tab>These days it seems there're more pests than people living in Stilltide, what with all the hopefuls running off to Eulmore.

TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_002<tab>Those flying lizards are the worst of the lot, though. You can't even leave for an honest day's work anymore without a swarm of them flapping sky demons nipping at your heels from here to Governor's Row.
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_003<tab>And don't get me started on their leader! “Jaculus,” we call him. With the way that vicious blighter comes after you, you'd think he bloody owns the place!
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_004<tab>Ugh, <var 1A 02 /var>someone<var 1A 01 /var> needs to topple that little tyrant. None of us fancy losing a finger, but maybe you're up to the challenge?
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_005<tab>If you're keen to draw him out, just skewer a couple of his broodmates. That'll get his attention soon enough.

TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_010<tab>Did you say you were going to gut that territorial lizard leader for us? Like I said, just murder some of his mates, and you'll soon get an audience with Jaculus himself.
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_020<tab>You got the bitey little bastard, then!? Shadows be praised! Now maybe we can work the fields in peace.
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_021<tab>If you hadn't done the deed, I was afraid we'd start running out of food. And I've no wish to watch anyone starve to death...
TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_022<tab>Aye, I know we could move to Gatetown and live on handouts of meol like the rest of them, but we have our pride.

TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_023<tab>It's not like we could just move to Gatetown and live on handouts of meol anymore. Did you know that stuff was the flesh of sin eaters? <shudder> No bloody thank you.

TEXT_LUCKZA008_03350_CATTY_000_024<tab>If there's any choice in the matter, we'd rather take care of our own needs while we can...with a little help from battle-savvy travelers such as yourself, of course!
